# Quality Calibration Sweep v2 - 2026-03-08
#
# Corpus: CID22-512 (209 images, 512x512)
# Quality levels: 26 (Q5..Q99)
# Codecs: libjpeg-turbo (baseline anchor), jpeg (jpegli), webp (zenwebp), avif (zenavif speed 10), jxl (zenjxl)
# Metric: SSIMULACRA2 via fast-ssim2
# Total measurements: 27,170 (5434 per codec, 26 JXL failures)
# Total time: 323s
# Command: cargo run --release --no-default-features --features calibrate --example quality_calibrate -- --corpus ~/work/codec-corpus/CID22/CID22-512/training --output /mnt/v/output/quality-calibrate-v2
#
# libjpeg-turbo config: quality 1-100 direct, 4:2:0 subsampling, no optimization
# jpegli: quality direct passthrough via with_generic_quality
# webp: quality direct passthrough via with_generic_quality
# avif: quality direct passthrough, effort=0 (speed 10, fastest)
# jxl: quality mapped via piecewise linear (Q90-100→d0-1, Q70-90→d1-2, Q0-70→d2-9)
